---
import { SHOP_URL, SHOP_LABEL, LINE_ID, LINE_URL } from "../config";
---

<aside class="article-aside" aria-label="選購與諮詢">
  <p class="article-aside__lead">
    若已大致選定口味或型號，可至<strong>{SHOP_LABEL}</strong>查看現貨、相容規格與選購說明；本站文章僅供閱讀參考，不以站內下單為目的。
  </p>
  <p class="article-aside__line">
    LINE ID：<a href={LINE_URL} rel="noopener noreferrer">{LINE_ID}</a>
    — 可協助確認口味、規格、現貨與售後諮詢。
  </p>
  <div class="article-aside__actions">
    <a class="btn btn--shop" href={SHOP_URL} rel="noopener noreferrer">前往{SHOP_LABEL}</a>
    <a class="btn btn--line" href={LINE_URL} rel="noopener noreferrer">加 LINE 諮詢</a>
  </div>
</aside>
